item.title: Conference Structure of MOSCMY 2017
item.description: Talk and Tutorials: There will be 24 talks and tutorial sessions Competition : There will be programming competitions for Enterprise Open Source solution. Demonstration Booth : There will be 20 booths for sponsors to exhibit and demonstrate their products, services and projects in detail to participants. Birds of a Feather : There will be Birds of a Feather sessions, where participants with the same interest can get together to have a lively dialogue about their Open Source project.
